The Ontology of DTD and C-PTSD 
10 May 2026

Keywords
Developmental Trauma Disorder (DTD); Complex Post-Traumatic Stress Disorder (C-PTSD) 
Preamble
Aim. I believe the way DTD and C-PTSD are described by laypeople and those who write articles on the subject leads to faulty conclusions [evidence?] due to the lack of understanding by the intended audience (laypeople). In this article I aim to elucidate the ontology of DTD and C-PTSD for all audiences with scientific backing.

